Cut through settings
------------------------------
<reg_public_text>:
Enable cut through forwarding for the port.
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Ingress speed of frames coming from the port, used for selecting between store and forward queing and cut-through queuing.
If the ingress speed is lower than the egress speed, the frame is enqueued at end of frame, otherwise at start of frame.
Egress speed is selected by XQS:QMAP_SE_TBL:QMAP_CT_ESP and XQS::FWD_CT_CFG.FWD_CT_ESP.
